name: Interpolation
body:
Interpolation
=============

Pavage d'espace en simplexe

### Compilation

```shell
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
```

### Lancement

```
$ ./build/src/exec -f [CHEMIN_VERS_LE_FICHIER_CSV]
```

Exemple :

```
$ ./build/src/exec -f ../../data/data11.csv
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
